reviewText: Another fantastic season of the George RR Martin Phenomenon.

I wanted to comment on the outrageous price for the Steelbox edition, which is roughly $30 more than the regular Blu_ray. For that you get some extras, a magnet (Whoopee) and Dolby Atmos. Simply ridiculous.

I also want to critisize Amazon for not indicating which of the myriad editions they sell have Dolby Atmos.

I have not watched this set yet
loved the limited edition set. Good quality.
Excellent series and enjoy the collector style of packaging.
